The chemical formula of 5-(methylsulfanylmethyl)piperidin-3-ol is C11H23NO2S. 
This formula consists of:
- 11 carbon atoms
- 23 hydrogen atoms
- 1 nitrogen atom
- 1 oxygen atom
- 1 sulfur atom

Therefore, the total number of atoms in 5-(methylsulfanylmethyl)piperidin-3-ol is 37.
